  "content": "<p>Get ready to dance the night away with Immortal Fruits, the hottest Nolimit City slot game in town! With 5 reels, 4 rows, and 50 fixed paylines, you'll be spinning those fruity reels like a pro. </p><p>But this isn't your grandma's fruit machine - oh no! This game has got a disco fever theme that'll have you grooving in your seat. Think Saturday Night Fever meets Las Vegas slots. </p>"
